ace. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And (tropical:)  A woman's ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head-covering such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximaAr","text_ar":"خِمَار"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, K, TA,) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qinaAE","text_ar":"قِنَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; occurring in a trad.; (Mgh, TA;) metaphorically applied thereto. (Mgh.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A crown, such as is worn by a king:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, K, * TA:) [said to be] so called because made of skins. (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garment of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jub~ap","text_ar":"جُبَّة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which the two sleeves have been tucked up."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b6-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The half of a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garment such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of the soft hair of camels;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"now known by the appellation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jbp","text_ar":"جبة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[evidently a mistranscription, app. for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xib~ap","text_ar":"خِبَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (TA.) ―         -b7-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bag such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wafoDap","text_ar":"وَفْضَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (K, TA,) [i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariyTap","text_ar":"خَرِيطَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which the beggar puts his alms."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And hence, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw Alfarowap","text_ar":"ذُو الفَرْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beggar."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b8-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A portion of herbage collected together and dry."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b9-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Waste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uncultivated, land, having in it no herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and no"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bara$","text_ar":"بَرَش"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"maculæ,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spots differing in colour from the rest"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw farowapK","text_ar":"اَبُو فَرْوَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bal~uwT","text_ar":"بَلُّوط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chestnut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is called in Egypt"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abw frwp","text_ar":"ابو فروة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the present day]; of the dial. of Egypt: it is thus called because within its husk is what resembles the soft hair of camels. (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"varowapN","text_ar":"ثَرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, As, ISk, T, S, M, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ginFY","text_ar":"غِنًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abundance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"richness"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.;] accord. to Yaakoob [i. e. ISk], (M,) formed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"varowapN","text_ar":"ثَرْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"by substitution (S, M) of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"f","text_ar":"ف"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"v","text_ar":"ث"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu la*uw varowapK mina AlmaAli","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَذُو ثَرْوَةٍ مِنَ المَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farowapK","text_ar":"فَرْوَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", both meaning the same [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is a possessor of abundance of property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (T, S; [in some copies of the latter,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlmaAli","text_ar":"فِى المَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) so says ISk, (T,) or Fr; (S;) and As says the like: (S:) the latter says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN *uw farowapK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ ذُو فَرْوَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"varowapK","text_ar":"ثَرْوَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is a possessor of abundant property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Lth","T","M","Mgh","TA","Fr","As","ISk"]}]}}